520
00:47:36,403 --> 00:47:39,114
They fell in love. It happens.

521
00:47:40,282 --> 00:47:42,910
Is he a good boy? I don't know.

522
00:47:43,410 --> 00:47:47,623
Is he from a good family? I don't know.

523
00:47:48,957 --> 00:47:52,002
