539
00:48:57,860 --> 00:48:58,861
Sure.

540
00:48:59,111 --> 00:49:01,155
Okay, let's go. Come on.

541
00:49:03,031 --> 00:49:04,032
Come here.

542
00:49:04,825 --> 00:49:05,951
What's the matter?

543
00:49:08,662 --> 00:49:12,499
I just feel like we can't get married,
not like this.

544
00:49:13,959 --> 00:49:14,960
It's like...

545
00:49:15,460 --> 00:49:17,421
when I'm with you...

546
00:49:17,504 --> 00:49:19,673
I am so happy...

547
00:49:20,632 --> 00:49:23,051
but my family is so unhappy.

548
00:49:23,510 --> 00:49:25,929
And our wedding should be
this joyous thing.

549
00:49:25,971 --> 00:49:28,891
But it won't be for them,
because it can't be in our church.

550
00:49:28,932 --> 00:49:32,853
So, let's just go somewhere.
Please, let's just go.

551
00:49:34,021 --> 00:49:36,690
Hey, I love you.

552
00:49:37,399 --> 00:49:38,650
Why?

553
00:49:39,443 --> 00:49:41,111
Why do you love me?

554
00:49:42,321 --> 00:49:44,698
Because I came alive when I met you.

555
00:49:46,533 --> 00:49:47,993
But my family....

556
00:49:50,120 --> 00:49:52,039
You're a part of your family...

557
00:49:53,540 --> 00:49:55,459
and I'll do anything...

558
00:49:56,877 --> 00:49:59,338
whatever it takes, to get them to accept me.

559
00:50:00,589 --> 00:50:03,258
Because you're my whole life now.

560
00:50:03,800 --> 00:50:06,970
We're not going to skulk off
and get married...

561
00:50:07,679 --> 00:50:09,389
as if we're ashamed of ourselves.

562
00:50:10,933 --> 00:50:11,934
Okay?

563
00:50:13,560 --> 00:50:14,520
Okay.

564
00:50:17,189 --> 00:50:18,398
Did you say "skulk"?

565
00:50:18,440 --> 00:50:21,610
-Shut up.
-Let's just skulk off somewhere....

566
00:50:25,364 --> 00:50:26,573
Come on, talk to him.

567
00:50:26,990 --> 00:50:28,534
Toula loves him.

568
00:50:28,742 --> 00:50:30,619
