673
00:59:31,660 --> 00:59:34,288
Dad, the thing is
that we just want to keep it small.

674
00:59:34,329 --> 00:59:37,791
It's like you'd rather go bankrupt
than insult anyone from the church.

675
00:59:38,000 --> 00:59:39,084
Toula...

676
00:59:39,543 --> 00:59:43,922
