with $8 in my pocket...

677
00:59:44,339 --> 00:59:46,675
to make all this for you.

678
00:59:47,342 --> 00:59:48,343
And...

679
00:59:49,720 --> 00:59:53,348
who knows how long I'm going to be alive?

680
00:59:55,601 --> 00:59:57,060
Let me see the list.

681
00:59:59,480 --> 01:00:02,107
Okay, come on. Time out!

682
01:00:02,691 --> 01:00:04,818
No more punching Thio Niko's nads, okay?

