686
01:00:14,828 --> 01:00:17,873
-Did she spit on him?
-Now go on, go outside with your father.

687
01:00:17,998 --> 01:00:21,168
Yeah, for good luck. Keeps the devil away.

688
01:00:21,960 --> 01:00:23,670
Bye. Wait for me.

689
01:00:25,130 --> 01:00:26,173
Dad.

690
01:00:29,343 --> 01:00:30,761
