693
01:00:40,187 --> 01:00:41,563
Okay, Niko.

694
01:00:42,022 --> 01:00:43,690
Ian, are you hungry?

695
01:00:43,941 --> 01:00:46,777
-No, I already ate.
-Okay, I'll make you something.

696
01:00:47,820 --> 01:00:48,904
Okay.

697
01:00:49,530 --> 01:00:52,991
Now, Toula,
we have to have Tommy Kasimatis.

698
01:00:55,369 --> 01:00:57,162
Hey, let me help you with those.

699
01:00:57,287 --> 01:01:00,123
-What is wrong with Tommy Kasimatis?
-I don't know them.

700
01:01:00,249 --> 01:01:03,252
-Who cares? They're related to me.
-Why are you being so weird?

701
01:01:03,335 --> 01:01:06,505
-I'm not being weird.
-You're weird when you're pregnant.

702
01:01:12,928 --> 01:01:14,471
Ian, eat.

703
01:01:17,391 --> 01:01:19,434
How do you say "thank you" in Greek?

704
01:01:22,688 --> 01:01:24,523
That's it. You got it.

705
01:01:39,872 --> 01:01:41,081
-Hey, Toula!
-Yeah?

706
01:01:41,290 --> 01:01:44,168
Listen, I got the greatest connection
for your invitations.

707
01:01:44,459 --> 01:01:46,879
No, we're gonna order
our own invitations, okay?

708
01:01:46,920 --> 01:01:49,631
I don't want something
your cash-only connection gets...

709
01:01:49,715 --> 01:01:51,133
that falls off of a truck.

710
01:01:51,258 --> 01:01:54,678
-Yeah, but they come through, right?
-For God's sake, let the man talk.

711
01:01:54,720 --> 01:01:57,181
-Why are you always so stubborn?
-I'm not stubborn--

712
01:01:58,640 --> 01:02:02,352
Girls, I ordered the invitations
two weeks ago.

713
01:02:03,604 --> 01:02:06,690
-I never saw a wedding invitation.
-I'll go get them.

714
01:02:14,781 --> 01:02:16,700
Wait till you see them.

715
01:02:29,087 --> 01:02:31,423
My parents' names are Rodney and Harriet.

716
01:02:33,634 --> 01:02:34,801
"Rodney and Harry"?

717
01:02:39,640 --> 01:02:41,683
I didn't notice, so I bet they won't.

718
01:02:41,809 --> 01:02:43,602
Yia sas, everybody.

719
01:02:44,311 --> 01:02:46,980
Wait. I have got the biggest scoop.

720
01:02:47,981 --> 01:02:52,402
Look at the earrings I have found
that match the bridesmaids' dresses.

721
01:02:53,028 --> 01:02:56,073
I remembered.
We have a customer at the dry cleaner's...

722
01:02:56,198 --> 01:02:58,200
who is a custom jewelry designer.

723
01:02:58,242 --> 01:03:00,244
So, I showed her the fabric.

724
01:03:00,369 --> 01:03:03,664
