Not that fabric you showed me last week.

725
01:03:03,789 --> 01:03:06,583
-You said you liked it.
-I said I'd think about it.

726
01:03:06,917 --> 01:03:08,669
That's just because...

727
01:03:10,921 --> 01:03:13,090
you couldn't visualize it.

728
01:03:15,300 --> 01:03:18,428
-You're so beautiful!
-Don't worry, you don't have to do a thing.

729
01:03:18,512 --> 01:03:19,471
That's classy.

730
01:03:21,890 --> 01:03:24,184
I went by the college and picked this up.

731
01:03:27,062 --> 01:03:28,105
Look.

732
01:03:29,690 --> 01:03:33,861
I'm gonna start slowly, you know.
Do a couple of night courses.

733
01:03:36,029 --> 01:03:40,742
I just wanted to learn more about painting
and art and stuff, so....

734
01:03:41,743 --> 01:03:43,787
This is so great.

735
01:03:44,872 --> 01:03:46,415
Yeah, you started it.

736
01:03:46,748 --> 01:03:48,750
You wanted to do something else...

737
01:03:49,960 --> 01:03:51,044
and you did it.

738
01:03:53,630 --> 01:03:54,590
Hey, Toula...

739
01:03:55,674 --> 01:03:58,010
don't let your past dictate who you are...

740
01:03:58,927 --> 01:04:01,889
but let it be part of who you will become.

741
01:04:03,390 --> 01:04:05,767
Nick, that is so beautiful.

742
01:04:06,143 --> 01:04:07,352
Yeah.

743
01:04:07,769 --> 01:04:11,064
That Dear Abby,
she really knows what she's talking about.

744
01:04:26,830 --> 01:04:29,249
-Hello?
-Hi, Mom, it's me.

745
01:04:30,292 --> 01:04:32,711
All right, Ian is going to pick me up...

746
01:04:32,753 --> 01:04:37,090
and then we'll get his parents,
and then we're gonna be there in one hour.

747
01:04:37,174 --> 01:04:38,342
-Good.
-Okay.

748
01:04:38,467 --> 01:04:41,428
