but they're my family.

1020
01:30:19,800 --> 01:30:21,552
We fight and we laugh.

1021
01:30:21,760 --> 01:30:24,429
And yes, we roast lamb on a spit
in the front yard.

1022
01:30:24,972 --> 01:30:27,391
And wherever I go, whatever I do...

1023
01:30:27,975 --> 01:30:29,685
they will always be there.

1024
01:30:37,109 --> 01:30:40,487
So, Ian and I moved into the house
my parents bought us.

1025
01:30:40,821 --> 01:30:42,531
A minute later, I was pregnant.

1026
01:30:42,614 --> 01:30:45,951
And six years later, it was our
daughter's turn to go to Greek school.

1027
01:30:46,034 --> 01:30:48,203
Mom, I want to go to Brownies.

1028
01:30:48,328 --> 01:30:50,581
I know, but I promise you this.

1029
01:30:50,831 --> 01:30:53,292
You can marry anybody you want.

1030
01:30:53,750 --> 01:30:55,627
Thanks, baby.

1031
01:30:56,170 --> 01:30:57,463
Greek school, pame.

1032
01:30:59,173 --> 01:31:00,174
What's that mean?

1033
01:31:00,299 --> 01:31:01,300
"Let's go."

1034
01:31:01,341 --> 01:31:03,010
-Let's go.
-That's pretty good.

1035
01:31:03,093 --> 01:31:04,595
-Looking good, Gus.
-Hi, Dad.

1036
01:31:04,720 --> 01:31:06,388
-Where you going?
-Greek school.

1037
01:31:07,097 --> 01:31:08,098
Baklava!

